<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; }
        .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
        .header { font-size: 24px; color: #004085; }
        .content { margin-top: 20px; }
        .footer { margin-top: 30px; font-size: 12px; color: #666; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">New Message from Your Personal Tutor</div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>Dear [Recipient Name],</p>
            <p>You have received a new message from your personal tutor, [Tutor Name].</p>
            <p><strong>Subject:</strong> [Message Subject]</p>
            <p>Please log in to the eTutor system to view the message.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>This is an automated notification. Please do not reply to this email.</p>
            <p>If you have any questions, please contact the support team.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>